Package config

package config
Configuration classes for the Internship Placement Management System.

This package contains Spring Boot configuration classes that set up the application environment, including web configuration, CORS settings, and other framework-level configurations.

Key Components:

  • WebConfig - Web MVC and CORS configuration for cross-origin requests

These configurations ensure the Spring Boot application can:

  • Accept requests from the React frontend (port 5173)
  • Configure HTTP methods and headers
  • Set up proper security and access controls
